{"tid":2279992,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［華爾街狠人］左媒有幾無恥？？","createTime":"2020-11-10T07:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T10:56:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"326f1865d40b739a0c3c86cb2869bb63cf609751","tid":2279992,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/FinanceFellow/photos/a.112035443472580/391556948853760/?type=3&amp;source=57&amp;refid=52&amp;__tn__=EH-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FFinanceFellow%2Fphotos%2Fa.112035443472580%2F391556948853760%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26source%3D57%26refid%3D52%26__tn__%3DEH-R&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=9ab22e98\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/FinanceFellow/photos/a.112035443472580/391556948853760/?type=3&amp;source=57&amp;refid=52&amp;__tn__=EH-R</a><br />\n<br />\n左媒有幾無恥？？<br />\n<br />\n當有對拜登不利的消息出現，左媒：不會報道，因為內容未經證實；就算總統直播都要Cut，要保障市民安全；未向當時人求證，一定是Fake News，要Ban。<br />\n<br />\n當有對拜登有利的消息出現，左媒：可以報道，消息由匿名人士提供；就算明明當時人已經公開回應，都唔當係Fake News，繼續出。<br />\n<br />\n第一夫人已經公開講明了自己立場，又有人立即留言指是「Fake News」，但CNN仍然繼續再出多個Post 老屈，企圖抹黑Trump為一個眾叛親離的惡棍。￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cnn/status/1325495559877177344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcnn%2Fstatus%2F1325495559877177344&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=89d6f222\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcnn%2Fstatus%2F1325495559877177344&h=b1662997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cnn/status/1325495559877177344</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/scottpresler/status/1325511497548779522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fscottpresler%2Fstatus%2F1325511497548779522&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=26e44eb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fscottpresler%2Fstatus%2F1325511497548779522&h=fef70acf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/scottpresler/status/1325511497548779522</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cnn/status/1325457330981511168\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcnn%2Fstatus%2F1325457330981511168&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=08f320ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcnn%2Fstatus%2F1325457330981511168&h=7ebd1985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cnn/status/1325457330981511168</a>"},{"pid":"687bf585d52db72c121ac9c7b45b6a8638ba2d97","tid":2279992,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkT8mbY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkT8mbY.jpg&h=19e701ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe8221059b0992cf7d6db05618b2fbc92128a8c3","tid":2279992,"uid":132572,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"所以侵由頭到尾<br />\n都無屌錯d 垃圾fake news"},{"pid":"a8998feea238020e903570ffd7d8a9db304001d6","tid":2279992,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f8afbe2d73e9fdd4f767658cc25c95874bd271","tid":2279992,"uid":29188,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6AOmbd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6AOmbd.gif&h=ab1d8ff0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ec443ce98f3723499f6467f78ae80d34d0e4ea2","tid":2279992,"uid":177485,"li